00:12:28,523 --> 00:12:33,587
And then at some point, I started to just play with color,

303
00:12:33,587 --> 00:12:37,169
play with mood, realizing that I was capturing some moments that

304
00:12:37,169 --> 00:12:39,351
were kind of isolated and whatnot.

