00:13:00,542 --> 00:13:02,863
And so all the while remembering

315
00:13:02,863 --> 00:13:04,404
that I never really put my stuff out there,

316
00:13:04,404 --> 00:13:07,104
and suddenly I have this confidence,

317
00:13:07,104 --> 00:13:09,465
slowly by slowly, to kind of level it up.

318
00:13:11,168 --> 00:13:14,131
And this was one of the more recent pictures I posted.

319
00:13:14,131 --> 00:13:18,394
And actually at the time, I looked at classic Blade Runner.

320
00:13:18,394 --> 00:13:19,936
I was trying to deconstruct what they did

321
00:13:19,936 --> 00:13:22,318
with their color palette.

