00:13:28,943 --> 00:13:30,785
I want to learn a new skill to,

326
00:13:30,785 --> 00:13:33,807
here's putting my stuff out there, bringing me out,

327
00:13:33,807 --> 00:13:35,789
being able to share my work.

328
00:13:35,789 --> 00:13:39,332
One of the things I realized that held me back was,

329
00:13:40,497 --> 00:13:42,059
all of the stuff I wanted to learn.

330
00:13:42,059 --> 00:13:43,300
And being able to get to that stage,

331
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:44,801
I knew that the only way to do it

332
00:13:44,801 --> 00:13:46,983
was to surround myself with people who knew it best.

333
00:13:46,983 --> 00:13:53,048
And so, again, I just wanted to see

334
00:13:53,048 --> 00:13:54,149
how far I could take that.

335
00:13:54,149 --> 00:13:57,092
And I started reaching out to different people

336
00:13:57,092 --> 00:13:58,993
because really what I wanted to learn about was portraiture.

337
00:13:58,993 --> 00:14:01,456
When you do street photography, it's quite like a,

338
00:14:01,456 --> 00:14:04,498
you know, it's like just me by myself,

