340
00:14:07,747 --> 00:14:10,089
And the thing I always struggled with was confidence,

341
00:14:10,089 --> 00:14:11,550
like face-to-face communication,

342
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:13,371
especially the anxiety that I would feel

343
00:14:13,371 --> 00:14:16,253
of just meeting somebody new for the first time.

