00:14:16,253 --> 00:14:19,615
And so I sent off all these different emails

345
00:14:19,615 --> 00:14:21,857
ahead of the next trips that I'd planned,

346
00:14:21,857 --> 00:14:25,779
whether it was LA or San Francisco or Vegas, Tokyo.

347
00:14:25,779 --> 00:14:28,241
And I had a lot of people reply.

348
00:14:31,055 --> 00:14:33,378
And so yeah, I was able to learn from these people

349
00:14:33,378 --> 00:14:34,380
because they'd been in situations

350
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:36,123
where they were already used to posing

351
00:14:36,123 --> 00:14:37,164
and I never had to worry about that.

352
00:14:37,164 --> 00:14:39,748
I could see how makeup artists worked.

353
00:14:39,748 --> 00:14:43,314
I could see how they held themselves for different shoots.

354
00:14:43,872 --> 00:14:45,814
all whilst knowing that I'd never really done that.

355
00:14:45,814 --> 00:14:49,637
These are actually, I never shot pictures of people at all

356
00:14:49,637 --> 00:14:54,741
before, maybe my nephew at his birthday.

357
00:14:54,741 --> 00:14:56,822
But suddenly I just had this confidence

358
00:14:56,822 --> 00:14:59,745
and I accepted the nervousness of like, you know what,

359
00:14:59,745 --> 00:15:00,866
I have nothing to lose,

360
00:15:00,866 --> 00:15:02,307
so I would just reach out to different people.

