00:15:03,392 --> 00:15:04,833
On the bottom right, you see my message.

362
00:15:04,833 --> 00:15:05,834
I go like, love your work.

363
00:15:05,834 --> 00:15:07,616
If you're ever in Montreal, let me know.

364
00:15:07,616 --> 00:15:08,376
Here's my link.

365
00:15:08,376 --> 00:15:09,837
Nothing more than that.

366
00:15:09,837 --> 00:15:12,179
Put it out there, and I think it was that mentality

367
00:15:12,179 --> 00:15:13,320
of like, you know, today, tomorrow.

368
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:15,382
Nothing in my life's really gonna change,

369
00:15:15,382 --> 00:15:17,224
so I might as well take that step,

370
00:15:17,224 --> 00:15:18,785
almost like tennis, and just serve it.

371
00:15:18,785 --> 00:15:22,328
And so what was cool is I got to meet these people,

372
00:15:22,328 --> 00:15:24,570
and they were really inspiring to me

373
00:15:24,570 --> 00:15:26,812
because these are people that all actually

